:h1 id='HELP_GENERAL' res=1000.General
:lines  align=center.
&PrgName. &Version.
:elines.
:p.:color fc='DarkBlue' bc='default'.Welcome to STris, which stands for Straub's
Tetris.:color fc='Default' bc='Default'.
:p.STris is my first project developed under OS/2. I was looking for a program
whereby I could learn the basics of OS/2 programming. As a great fan of
Tetris-style games I was somewhat disappointed by the existing versions that I
had found, so I decided to write one myself. 
:p.If you are an old-fashioned Amiga-user (like me) you may recognize some
parallels to "WBTris", which was written by Dirk Bîhmer and Ralf Pieper.   
:lines.
:lm margin=30.
:p.Have fun with &PrgName. 
:p.
