:i1.Installation
:color fc='DarkBlue' bc='default'.Installation:color fc='Default' bc='Default'.
:elines.
:p.If you are reading this text you have already installed &PrgName.
successfully. So there is no need to lose a lot of words about the installation
procedure.    
:h1 id='HELP_UNINSTALLING' res=3300.Uninstallation
:lines  align=center.
:font facename='Helv' size=0x0.

:i1.Uninstalling
:color fc='DarkBlue' bc='default'.Uninstalling:color fc='Default' bc='Default'.
:elines.
:p.I can't believe it. You really want to throw &PrgName. away. Nothing easier
than that. &PrgName. does not need any 
:i1.DLL
DLL's and it does not modify your 
:i1.CONFIG.SYS
CONFIG.SYS or any other system files. If you want to get rid of &PrgName. you
can simply delete it's directory and the 
:i1.WPS Object
WPS Object created by the Installscript.    
:h1 id='HELP_HOWTOPLAY' res=4000.How to play
:lines  align=center.
:font facename='Helv' size=0x0.

:i1.How to play
:color fc='DarkBlue' bc='default'.How to play:color fc='Default' bc='Default'.
:elines.
:p.Hey, you really want to tell me that you don't know how to play Tetris. You
must be kidding.  
:p.The main goal in this type of games is to navigate the falling pieces so that
they fill up horizontal lines. If a line is entirely filled it disappears and
you get lots of points. Removing more than one line at a time will double the
given score. So try to fill up as many lines as possible. More points can also
be gained by starting in a higher level or with higher speed.
:p.The falling piece is controlled with the cursor keys. You can move the piece
left/right and you can rotate it. As the game goes on the falling speed of the
pieces increases. :link reftype=hd res=4100.Click here :elink.to see more 
information about the key-bindings.
:p.The game ends when there is no more room for a new piece.
:p.So I think that's all you need to know for the moment. Any more questions ?  
